						               													<description>Flintloque Reloaded is a 2nd edition rule book for Flintloque after Deadloque (2nd edition) with some changes to the rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As with the previous editions Flintloque is a Fantasy Black powder skirmish war game rules which each fantasy race take the part of one of the nations of Valon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flintloque Reloaded is a set of stand alone rules with everything you need to play Flintloque, but it is missing a few of the Undead rules so you will still need a copy of Deadloque (Second Edition) if you want to play them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The major changes from Deadloque (2nd edition) is that a skills system been added, an additional column for movement (falter), wounds are calculated differently, a points system and artillery rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flintloque Reloaded was available either by it self of with a box set of miniatures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
